steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi004" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi004" display
When I add new column with Name "jitapicol004" Type "string" for Table name "jitapi004"
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "jitapi004s" from list
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitapi004s/:id"
When I click tab "Request params" in Params of floating panel
When I delete params row "1"
Then I should NOT see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "id","String".
When I click tab "Response params" in Params of floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitapi004s"
When I delete params row "5"
Then I should NOT see floating panel has Params - row "5" - value "jitapicol004","Column Definition","jitapicol004"
When I close the floating panel
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitapi004s/:id"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - DefinitionValue Table - row "1" - value "jitapi004s.id","request.id"
